  "macro_observations_html": "\n<style>\n.rwa-gmo-takeaways {\n  border: 1px solid #C7D8E8;\n  border-radius: 10px;\n  padding: 0.9rem 1.05rem 1rem;\n  margin: 0.15rem 0 0.5rem;\n  background: #ffffff;\n  box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(15,23,42,0.06);\n}\n.rwa-gmo-takeaways ul {\n  margin: 0.35rem 0 0.25rem 1.1rem;\n  padding: 0;\n  color: #1F4C67;\n  font-size: 0.92rem;\n  line-height: 1.45;\n}\n.rwa-gmo-takeaways li {\n  margin-bottom: 0.45rem;\n}\n.rwa-gmo-takeaways ul ul {\n  margin: 0.2rem 0 0.1rem 0.85rem;\n  padding: 0;\n  list-style-type: disc;\n}\n.rwa-gmo-takeaways ul ul li {\n  margin-bottom: 0.3rem;\n}\n.rwa-gmo-takeaways .rwa-gmo-takeaway-note {\n  margin: 0.55rem 0 0 0;\n  font-size: 0.78rem;\n  color: #3E6A7A;\n  line-height: 1.4;\n}\n</style>\n<div class=\"rwa-gmo-takeaways\">\n  <ul>\n    <li><strong>Institutional momentum.</strong> Large asset managers, banks, and market utilities are scaling tokenized\n    cash funds, bonds, and repo-style workflows\u2014often on permissioned networks first\u2014while public-ledger RWA issuance\n    keeps expanding in parallel.</li>\n    <li><strong>2030 market size (estimates only; not apples-to-apples).</strong>\n      <ul>\n        <li><a href=\"https://www.mckinsey.com/industries/financial-services/our-insights/from-ripples-to-waves-the-transformational-power-of-tokenizing-assets\">McKinsey &amp; Company</a> (June&nbsp;2024): <strong>~$2&nbsp;trillion</strong>\n        tokenized financial-asset market cap by <strong>2030</strong> (central case); about <strong>$1\u20134&nbsp;trillion</strong> across\n        published scenarios; excludes major crypto and stablecoins to avoid double counting.</li>\n        <li><a href=\"https://www.addx.co/files/bcg_ADDX_report_Asset_tokenization_trillion_opportunity_by_2030_de2aaa41a4.pdf\">Boston Consulting Group</a> (with ADDX): widely cited\n        <strong>~$16&nbsp;trillion</strong> framing for <strong>illiquid-asset</strong> tokenization potential by <strong>2030</strong>\n        (see joint report PDF; scope is broader than McKinsey\u2019s tokenized-financial-assets slice).</li>\n        <li><a href=\"https://www.citigroup.com/rcs/citigpa/storage/public/GPS_Report_Stablecoins_2030.pdf\">Citigroup</a> (GPS, <em>Stablecoins 2030</em>, 2025 refresh): bank\n        scenario work summarized in the press points to roughly <strong>~$1.9&nbsp;trillion (base) to ~$4&nbsp;trillion (bull)</strong>\n        for <strong>stablecoin-related</strong> market size by <strong>2030</strong>\u2014definitions are payment-rail / bank-token\n        oriented, not \u201call RWAs.\u201d</li>\n        <li><a href=\"https://reports.weforum.org/docs/WEF_Asset_Tokenization_in_Financial_Markets_2025.pdf\">World Economic Forum</a> (2025, <em>Asset Tokenization in Financial\n        Markets</em>): cites industry projections that global private equity / venture capital <strong>could reach ~$7&nbsp;trillion\n        by 2030</strong>, with discussion that <strong>~10%</strong> might be tokenized\u2014one asset-class lens inside a wider survey\n        of markets and policy.</li>\n      </ul>\n    </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p class=\"rwa-gmo-takeaway-note\">Snapshot for context only (not investment advice). The chart and table below reflect\n  RWA.xyz homepage data, not the third-party forecasts above.</p>\n</div>\n<p class=\"review-note ko-disclaimer\">Key observations are AI generated and should be reviewed for accuracy.</p>",
